# <center>Mi Card</center>

## :clipboard: Features
**Mi Card** is a simple application considered as User Profile card. The application build for both Android and iOS using a single codebase, ***Flutter***.

Features available:

- [x] Interactive UI
- [x] Circular Profile Avatar
- [x] Dark Theme
- [x] Awesome Icons
- [x] GitHub Icon Button

## :gear: Prerequisites
* Flutter
* Dart
* IDE
    * Android Studio (*Recommend*)
    * Visual Studio Code
    * Xcode (*Mac*)

## :envelope_with_arrow: Install
* Flutter : [Flutter](https://flutter.dev/)
